metadata.name: The Dance of Jellyfish - Black | White
metadata.description:
In a surreal scenario, outside my window dancing jellyfish accompany my journey.

Each image was made using Adobe Illustrator program with crop mask function.
The collection of jellyfish photos was taken with my Canon 550d at the Genoa Aquarium.

Size 12601 × 16801
Focal Length 28mm
F number f/22
Exposure time 1/50
